headline: Hubbell launches modular, scalable software that transforms utility operations
summary: Hubbell Incorporated continues to define the future of utility operations with today's launch of Aclara360™, a dynamic new software solution that unlocks the full potential of grid-edge device data. The modular system from its Aclara brand equips utilities to use advanced grid analytics to make quicker, smarter network decisions – all without major capital investment.
